data.description: Welcome home to this fabulous row-end townhome nestled in the heart of North Salt Lake. This meticulously maintained property boasts tasteful updates throughout, offering a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the spacious living areas adorned with contemporary finishes and a simplistic design that exudes sophistication. One of the standout features of this gem is the impressive tall ceilings found on every level, including the garage, creating an open and airy atmosphere throughout the home.With three bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this residence is thoughtfully designed to provide both functionality and style. The modernized touches throughout the home add a touch of luxury, making it a delightful place to call home.Situated within the community, this townhome strategically captures stunning views of the east mountains, providing a picturesque backdrop for your daily life. The location ensures a peaceful and quiet living experience, making it thoroughly enjoyable for residents seeking tranquility.Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule a showing today to experience the charm and warmth of this North Salt Lake townhome. All information provided is offered as a courtesy, and buyers and agents are encouraged to verify all details to ensure a seamless transaction.
